Life Channeler									KEY:Druid Archetype ~ Life Channeler								CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.DruidArchetype																																																				PREALIGN:LN,TN,CN,LE,NE,CE	PRECLASS:1,Druid=1												PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Druid Archetype ~ Life Channeler],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Druid_Archetype_NatureBond=True,Druid_Archetype_WildShape=True,Druid_Archetype_VenomImmunity=True]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:Life channelers take the natural cycle to what they believe is its logical conclusion. By sacrificing the life of a sentient creature, they can generate energy that guarantees fertility and prosperity for lower creatures like plants and animals. These druids preach to flocks who become willing sacrifices, each serving as a "king" or "queen" for a short time after being chosen as the next sacrifice.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Life Channeler ~ Alignment|PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Life Channeler ~ Plant Preservation|PRECLASS:1,Druid=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Life Channeler ~ Wicker Talismans|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Life Channeler ~ Rampant Growth|PRECLASS:1,Druid=4	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Life Channeler ~ Stored Life|PRECLASS:1,Druid=9																																																																																																																																																																																													