Living Grimoire									KEY:Inquisitor Archetype ~ Living Grimoire							CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.InquisitorArchetype																																																								PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=1												PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Inquisitor Archetype ~ Living Grimoire],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Inquisitor_Archetype_MonsterLore=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_Spells=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_CunningInitiative=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_Judgment=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_Bane=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_SecondJudgment=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_GreaterBane=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_ThirdJudgment=True,Inquisitor_Archetype_TrueJudgment=True]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												DESC:The living grimoire literally wields the sacred word of his deity, using his holy tome to smite the foes of his god with divine might. Unlike most inquisitors, a living grimoire focuses on careful study of divine scripture, valuing knowledge over intuition.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Living Grimoire ~ Holy Book|PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Living Grimoire ~ Spells|PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Living Grimoire ~ Sacred Word|PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Living Grimoire ~ Blessed Script|PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Living Grimoire ~ Word of God|PRECLASS:1,Inquisitor=20																																																																																																	