Soul Sentinel									KEY:Paladin Archetype ~ Soul Sentinel								CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.PaladinArchetype																																																								PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1												PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Paladin Archetype ~ Soul Sentinel],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy6=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfJustice=True,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy12=True]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:In a world of horrors, some holy warriors fight to safeguard the minds and spirits of those exposed to evil. Soul sentinels use the strength of their resolve to stem the tide of corruption and insanity, as they believe that the greatest tragedy is a soul lost to evil when it was within their power to save it.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Soul Sentinel ~ Reprieve|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Soul Sentinel ~ Sacred Soul|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=11	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Soul Sentinel ~ Greater Reprieve|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=12																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						