Tortured Crusader									KEY:Paladin Archetype ~ Tortured Crusader								CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.PaladinArchetype																																																								PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1												PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Paladin Archetype ~ Tortured Crusader],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Paladin_Archetype_Spells=True,Paladin_Archetype_SmiteEvil=True,Paladin_Archetype_LayOnHands=True,Paladin_Archetype_ClassSkills=True,Paladin_Archetype_DetectEvil=True,Paladin_Archetype_DivineGrace=True,Paladin_Archetype_ChannelPositiveEnergy=True,Paladin_Archetype_DivineBond=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfCourage=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfResolve=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfFaith=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfRighteousness=True,Paladin_Archetype_Mercy=True,Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfJustice=True]																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		DESC:Though tortured crusaders may be beaten and battered, body, mind, and soul, they still somehow continue through torment and hardship. Despite setbacks and impossible odds, they shine like candles even in the darkest times. Somewhere in their minds, they realize that they can't win in the end, but this only strengthens their resolve to fight for what is right, rather than giving in to hopelessness.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ Torment|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ Self-Sufficient|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ All Is Darkness|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ Alone in the Dark|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ Second Chance|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Tortured Crusader ~ Last Stand|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=11																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.65																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														FACT:Paladin_Archetype_Spells|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_SmiteEvil|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_LayOnHands|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_DetectEvil|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_DivineGrace|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_ChannelPositiveEnergy|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_DivineBond|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfCourage|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfResolve|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfFaith|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfRighteousness|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_Mercy|true	FACT:Paladin_Archetype_AuraOfJustice|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_DetectEvil|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_ClassSkills|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_DivineGrace|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_BondedMount|true	FACT:Paladin_CF_AuraOfJustice|true

#Martyr
Stigmata										KEY:Martyr ~ Stigmata											CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.MartyrClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								DESC:As a standard action,|!PRECLASS:1,Paladin=7	DESC:As a move action,|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=7|!PRECLASS:1,Paladin=13	DESC:As a swift action,|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=13	DESC:the martyr can chant hymns of faith and cause bleeding stigmata to visibly appear on his body. He can use this ability %1 rounds per day. While his stigmata are active, he takes 1 point of bleed damage, which automatically ceases when he ends this ability but otherwise does not relent, even in the face of magical healing or Heal checks. His stigmata assist his allies, duplicating the effect of the countersong, distraction,|3+CHA+PaladinLVL	DESC:or inspire courage|!PRECLASS:1,Paladin=10	DESC:inspire courage, or inspire greatness|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=10|!PRECLASS:1,Paladin=16	DESC:inspire courage, inspire greatness, or inspire heroics|PRECLASS:1,Paladin=16	DESC:bardic performance of a bard of his paladin level, though both countersong and distraction use Heal skill checks instead of Perform skill checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.64
See No Evil, Hear No Evil							KEY:Martyr ~ See No Evil Hear No Evil								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.MartyrClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:The martyr and all allies within 20 feet of him gain a +4 morale bonus on saving throws against bardic performance, sonic effects, language-dependent effects, and gaze attacks. This ability functions only when the martyr is conscious.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.64
Aura Mastery									KEY:Martyr ~ Aura Mastery										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.MartyrClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:The martyr's aura of courage, aura of resolve, and aura of righteousness have a radius of 20 feet instead of 10 feet, but the martyr does not gain immunity to fear, charms, or compulsions from those abilities. This ability alters aura of courage, aura of resolve, and aura of righteousness.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.64
Aura of Health									KEY:Martyr ~ Aura of Health										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.MartyrClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:The martyr and all allies within 20 feet of him gain a +4 morale bonus on saving throws against diseases. This ability functions only when the martyr is conscious.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.64
Martyr's Mercy									KEY:Martyr ~ Martyr's Mercy										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.MartyrClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:A martyr can apply any of the mercies for which he qualifies based on his paladin level to his lay on hands, even if he didn't select that mercy (or its prerequisites). However, when he uses a mercy he didn't select, he transfers the condition to himself for the remaining duration (ignoring any immunity he might have to the condition), and he can't use this ability if he already has that condition. If he transfers a condition to himself in this way, he can't remove it from himself with a personal-only ability. The martyr can use lay on hands on any ally within 30 feet, rather than needing to touch the ally, but using lay on hands on himself is a standard action, not a swift action. This ability alters lay on hands and mercy.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.64

#Soul Sentinel
Reprieve										KEY:Soul Sentinel ~ Reprieve										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.SoulSentinelClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:A soul sentinel relieves manic and tortured souls exposed to the harsh evil of the world. When the soul sentinel uses her lay on hands ability to heal a living creature, she can remove confusion effects in place of applying one of her other mercies. If used on a creature suffering from a permanent confusion effect, this removes the effect for only 1 minute.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.65
Sacred Soul										KEY:Soul Sentinel ~ Sacred Soul									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.SoulSentinelClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:A sacred soul is immune to hexes and curse spells or abilities. Each ally within 10 feet of her gains a +4 morale bonus on saving throws against hexes or curses. This ability functions only while the paladin is conscious, not if she is unconscious or dead.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.65
Greater Reprieve									KEY:Soul Sentinel ~ Greater Reprieve								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Paladin Class Feature.SoulSentinelClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:The soul sentinel suppresses the stain of corruption on the spirits of those she heals. Whenever she uses her lay on hands ability to heal a living creature (other than herself) or damage an undead creature, in place of applying one of her other mercies, she can suppress the stain from a corrupted creature's most recent manifestation for 1 minute (for more information about corruption and manifestations, see page 14). Any gift from that manifestation is unaffected and remains available, unless the manifestation has a special note requiring the gift and stain be taken together, in which case greater reprieve also suppresses the gift.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.65

