Cruel Tricks									KEY:Bloody Jake ~ Cruel Tricks			SORTKEY:BloodyJake_CruelTrick_1	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.BloodyJakeClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								DESC:Bloody jakes use backwoods folk magic to confuse, terrify, and weaken their prey. A bloody jake can use this ability %1 times per day. He gains the cruel tricks below at the indicated slayer levels.|SlayerLVL+CHA																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.66	ASPECT:CheckCount|%1|SlayerLVL+CHA	ASPECT:CheckType|Uses per day
Distant Voices									KEY:Bloody Jake ~ Distant Voices			SORTKEY:BloodyJake_CruelTrick_2	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.BloodyJakeClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:A bloody jake can cause his voice to seem to emanate from somewhere else, as per ventriloquism. This ability doesn't take any other action to activate and can be used as part of speaking (as a free action); it costs one use of cruel tricks to affect his speech for 1 round.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.66
Lose Your Way									KEY:Bloody Jake ~ Lose Your Way			SORTKEY:BloodyJake_CruelTrick_3	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.BloodyJakeClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:As a standard action, a bloody jake can spend one use of cruel tricks to cause a creature that is within 30 feet and within the bloody jake's favored terrain to become disoriented, taking a -%1 penalty on Survival checks and a -2 penalty on saving throws against fear and illusions. This effect lasts for %1 hours of the bloody jake or for as long as the affected creature remains within the bloody jake's favored terrain, whichever is shorter.|SlayerLVL																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.66
