#Family Hunter
Find Family										KEY:Family Hunter ~ Find Family									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.FamilyHunterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																						DESC:A family hunter chooses a particular family line of mortal creatures to cleanse (she must choose an actual family line like "The Montrose family," rather than something generic that would cover all creatures of a given kind like "All humans descended from the first human created by the gods"). She can target any creature from that family line with discern next of kin (ACG) (with a caster level equal to her slayer level) at will as a spell-like ability. The save DC is Charisma-based and is modified by the slayer's studied target bonus if the creature is also her studied target. A creature that successfully saves against this effect is immune to this ability for 24 hours. If the family hunter's chosen family line is completely eradicated, she can choose a new one after 1 month of studying.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.66
Kinslayer										KEY:Family Hunter ~ Kinslayer										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.FamilyHunterClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:A family hunter's sneak attack deals an additional 1d6 points of damage to any creature with a blood relation to the family line she seeks to cleanse. This ability alters sneak attack.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.66
Studied Target									KEY:Family Hunter ~ Studied Target									CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.FamilyHunterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:A slayer can maintain more than one studied target at a time only if all targets are closely related to one another (even if they aren't part of the family line she seeks to cleanse). This includes blood relatives; undead spawn; constructs or undead and their creator; summoned creatures and their summoner; creatures that are charmed, dominated, or otherwise under direct magical control and their controller; and cohorts, followers, animal companions, familiars, and similar associates of one master. This ability alters studied target.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.67
Disrupt Teamwork									KEY:Family Hunter ~ Disrupt Teamwork								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Slayer Class Feature.FamilyHunterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					DESC:A family hunter's studied target never counts as an ally to its allies for the purpose of flanking the family hunter or using teamwork feats or the aid another action against the family hunter.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.67

