Cantrips										KEY:Tatterdemalion ~ Cantrips										CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Witch Class Feature.TatterdemalionClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							DESC:A tatterdemalion must choose mage hand, open/close, and prestidigitation as her prepared cantrips at 1st level, and they require a piece of cloth, string, rope, or other woven material (including clothing) as a focus. Any action she takes with these cantrips must involve the focus. Starting at 2nd level, she can choose any cantrip for her remaining cantrip. This alters the witch's cantrips.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.73
